sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeGW as KServe Gateway<br/>(Platform-managed)
    participant DrogonHTTP as Drogon HTTP Server<br/>REST port/TCP
    participant gRPCServer as gRPC Server<br/>gRPC port/TCP
    participant APIHandler as HttpRestApiHandler<br/>(API Key Validation)
    participant KFSImpl as KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    participant MPExecutor as MediaPipe Graph<br/>Executor
    participant LLMCalc as LLM Calculator<br/>(GenAiServable)
    participant GenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>Pipeline
    participant ModelMgr as Model Manager
    participant ModelInst as ModelInstance<br/>(OpenVINO Runtime)
    participant CloudSDK as Cloud SDK<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)
    participant CloudStore as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 1: REST - OpenAI Chat Completions (Streaming)
    Client->>KServeGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KServeGW->>DrogonHTTP: Forward request<br/>(Platform routing)
    DrogonHTTP->>APIHandler: Route to handler<br/>(API key validation)
    APIHandler->>MPExecutor: Dispatch to MediaPipe<br/>graph
    MPExecutor->>LLMCalc: Execute LLM Calculator
    LLMCalc->>GenAI: ContinuousBatchingPipeline<br/>or LLMPipeline
    GenAI-->>LLMCalc: Generated tokens (streaming)
    LLMCalc-->>MPExecutor: Token stream
    MPExecutor-->>DrogonHTTP: SSE stream
    DrogonHTTP-->>Client: data: {"choices":[...]}<br/>HTTP SSE

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 2: gRPC - KServe v2 Inference
    Client->>gRPCServer: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    gRPCServer->>KFSImpl: Dispatch to<br/>KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    KFSImpl->>ModelMgr: Get model instance
    ModelMgr->>ModelInst: Execute inference<br/>(OpenVINO Runtime)
    ModelInst-->>KFSImpl: Inference result
    KFSImpl-->>gRPCServer: ModelInferResponse
    gRPCServer-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 3: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    ModelMgr->>CloudSDK: getFilesystem(s3://, gs://, az://)
    CloudSDK->>CloudStore: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: IAM/SAS/ADC
    CloudStore-->>CloudSDK: Model files
    CloudSDK-->>ModelMgr: Local model cache
    ModelMgr->>ModelInst: Compile model<br/>(OpenVINO Core)

    Note over Client,CloudStore: Flow 4: DAG Pipeline Inference
    Client->>DrogonHTTP: POST /v1/models/{dag}:predict
    DrogonHTTP->>APIHandler: Route + auth
    APIHandler->>ModelMgr: EntryNode
    ModelMgr->>ModelInst: DLNode (inference)
    Note right of ModelInst: CustomNode (dlopen)<br/>executes user library
    ModelInst-->>ModelMgr: ExitNode result
    ModelMgr-->>DrogonHTTP: Response
    DrogonHTTP-->>Client: JSON prediction
